'''羅拔·柏迪臣'''（{{lang-en|Robert Pattinson}}，{{bd|1986年|5月13日<ref name="People">{{Cite news|title=Robert Pattinson|url=http://www.people.com/people/robert_pattinson|work=People|accessdate=2009-04-03|archive-date=2010-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100729183324/http://www.people.com/people/robert_pattinson|dead-url=no}}</ref>|||catIdx=P}}），全名'''羅拔·道格拉斯·湯瑪士·柏迪臣'''（{{lang-en|Robert Douglas Thomas Pattinson}}），是一位[[英國|英國]][[男演員|男演員]]。<ref name="LA Times">{{Cite news|author=Gina McIntyre|title=Robert Pattinson on his 'Twilight' songs: 'Music is my backup plan if acting fails'|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/herocomplex/2008/10/robert-pattin-1.html|work=Los Angeles Times|date=2008-10-09|accessdate=2009-02-01|archive-date=2010-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100605215134/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/herocomplex/2008/10/robert-pattin-1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

羅拔因演出2005年電影《[[哈利波特－火盃的考驗_(電影)|哈利波特－火盃的考驗]]》中的[[塞德里克·迪戈里|西追·迪戈里]]一角而開展他的銀幕事業<ref>{{Cite news|author=Sona Charaipotra|title=A Night Out With Robert Pattinson|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/11/16/fashion/16nite.html?_r=1&ref=movies|work=New York Times|date=2008-11-14|accessdate=2009-02-11|archive-date=2013-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511202807/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/11/16/fashion/16nite.html?_r=1&ref=movies|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來他因從[[史蒂芬妮·梅爾|史蒂芬妮·梅爾]]的小說改編的《[[暮光之城系列|暮光之城系列]]》電影中得到男主角[[愛德華·庫倫|愛德華·庫倫]]的角色而廣為人熟悉<ref>{{cite web|author=Rebecca Murray|title=Robert Pattinson Discusses 'Twilight'|url=http://movies.about.com/od/twilight/a/twilight073108.htm|publisher=About.com|date=2008-07-31|accessdate=2009-02-11|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081218045333/http://movies.about.com/od/twilight/a/twilight073108.htm|archivedate=2008-12-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Hillary Atkin|title=Exclusive Interview: Robert Pattinson|url=http://www.fandango.com/commentator_exclusiveinterview:robertpattinson_203|publisher=Fandango|date=2008-11-16|accessdate=2009-02-11|archive-date=2010-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100606081521/http://www.fandango.com/commentator_exclusiveinterview:robertpattinson_203|dead-url=no}}</ref>，系列电影包括於2008-2012年間的5部電影，全球票房收入合共超過$33億，從而帶來享譽世界，也建立了他在[[好萊塢|好萊塢]]中成為最高片酬和最叫座的演員之一的地位<ref name="Vanity Fair">{{cite web|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/features/2010/03/top-hollywood-earners-201003|title=Peter Newcomb on the Top Hollywood Earners of 2009|date=March 2010|work=Vanity Fair|author=Peter Newcomb|accessdate=2010-07-10|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100724175414/http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/features/2010/03/top-hollywood-earners-201003|archivedate=2010-07-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author=Dorothy Pomerantz |url=http://www.forbes.com/pictures/mfl45giih/robert-pattinson/#gallerycontent |title=Robert Pattinson |publisher=Forbes |date= |accessdate=2012-03-10 |archive-date=2020-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417044140/https://www.forbes.com/pictures/mfl45giih/robert-pattinson/#gallerycontent |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Hollywood's Best Actors for the Buck|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/dorothypomerantz/2011/12/06/hollywoods-best-actors-for-the-buck/|publisher=Forbes|first=Dorothy|last=Pomerantz|date=2011-12-06|accessdate=2012-08-10|archive-date=2020-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200221020744/https://www.forbes.com/sites/dorothypomerantz/2011/12/06/hollywoods-best-actors-for-the-buck/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年，羅拔被《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》選為「[[时代百大人物|時代最具影響力世上100人]]」之一，亦於同年被《[[富比士|富比士]]》列入「[[世界百大名人權力榜|世界百大名人權力榜]]」中，即世上最具影響力的名人之一<ref name="time">{{Cite news |author=Chris Weitz |title=The 2010 Time 100: Robert Pattinson |url=http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,1984685_1984940_1984948,00.html#ixzz0mUOIhqVr |work=Time |date=2010-04-29 |accessdate=2010-05-02 |archive-date=2010-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100502133329/http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,1984685_1984940_1984948,00.html#ixzz0mUOIhqVr |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="forbes1">{{cite news|title=The Celebrity 100: No.50 Robert Pattinson|url=http://www.forbes.com/lists/2010/53/celeb-100-10_Robert-Pattinson_TZ0B.html|work=Forbes|date=2010-06-28|accessdate=2012-08-10|archive-date=2019-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191030125632/https://www.forbes.com/lists/2010/53/celeb-100-10_Robert-Pattinson_TZ0B.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

電影方面，自《[[暮光之城系列|暮光之城系列]]》完結後，羅拔涉足於小成本製作的[[獨立電影|獨立電影]]，在《達利和他的情人》（2009）中飾演[[薩爾瓦多·達利|薩爾瓦多·達利]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://teaser-trailer.com/little-ashes-movie-with-robert-pattinson-as-dali/ |title=Little Ashes Movie With Robert Pattinson as Dali |access-date=2016-11-08 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225230745/https://teaser-trailer.com/little-ashes-movie-with-robert-pattinson-as-dali/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年，他於講述一個關於演員的名氣與人氣的紀錄片《Robsessed》中演出<ref name="MTV" />。2010年，他在《[[記得我|驚動了愛情]]》中，飾演一名充滿著困擾的年輕人<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.altfg.com/film/most-influential-people/ |title=Most Influential People Robert Pattinson, Lady Gaga & Ashton Kutcher? |access-date=2016-11-08 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225210442/https://www.altfg.com/film/most-influential-people/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他也在浪漫愛情電影《[[大象的眼淚|大象的眼淚]]》（2011）中演出<ref name="WFE" />。2012年，他在[[大衛·柯能堡|大衛·柯能堡]]的電影《{{le|夢遊大都會|Cosmopolis (film)}}》中，飾演一名硬朗、冷酷及懂計算的億萬富翁，電影為他贏得極高的讚譽<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/article/58878.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-08-13 |archive-date=2017-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170322102818/http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/article/58878.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年，他在充滿未來感的西部電影《{{link-en|絕命正義|The Rover (2014 film)}}》中演出<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://variety.com/2014/film/reviews/cannes-film-review-the-rover-1201183127/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-11-08 |archive-date=2019-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209013910/https://variety.com/2014/film/reviews/cannes-film-review-the-rover-1201183127/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，再度得到影評人的欣賞。同年，他亦為電影《{{link-en|寂寞星圖|Maps to the Stars}}》演出<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/filmreviews/10838381/Cannes-2014-Maps-to-the-Stars-review-a-nightmare-you-dont-want-to-wake-from.html |title=Maps to the Stars, review: 'a nightmare you don't want to wake from' |access-date=2016-11-08 |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309052116/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/filmreviews/10838381/Cannes-2014-Maps-to-the-Stars-review-a-nightmare-you-dont-want-to-wake-from.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>；2015年，他於傳記電影《沙漠女王》中演出，也在關於《[[生活_(雜誌)|生活]]》的攝影師丹尼斯·史托克與[[占士·甸|占士·甸]]的戲劇電影《[[叛逆年代|叛逆年代]]》中演出。2017年，他於[[詹姆士·葛雷|詹姆士·葛雷]]的電影《[[失落之城_(電影)|失落之城]]》中演出，那是關於一個[[侍從官|侍從官]]在尋找一個失落了的古城繼而在亞馬遜失蹤的故事<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.indiewire.com/2013/11/robert-pattinson-joins-james-grays-lost-city-of-z-with-benedict-cumberbatch-92066/ |title=-{Robert Pattinson Joins James Gray’s ‘Lost City Of Z’ With Benedict Cumberbatch}- |access-date=2016-11-08 |archive-date=2021-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226170448/https://www.indiewire.com/2013/11/robert-pattinson-joins-james-grays-lost-city-of-z-with-benedict-cumberbatch-92066/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以及在{{le|薩夫迪兄弟|Safdie brothers}}的電影《[[失速夜狂奔|失速夜狂奔]]》裡演出。

羅拔·柏迪臣於12歲便開始其模特兒的事業。2013年，[[迪奧男裝|迪奧男裝]]與他簽約成為旗下香水品牌的代言人。2016年，他還成為該品牌男裝系列的形象大使<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/robert-pattinsons-dior-homme-campaign-2017-black-carpet-collection-988503|title=ROBERT PATTINSON'S LATEST DIOR HOMME ADS HAVE ARRIVED|accessdate=2017-03-29|archive-date=2017-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170330010037/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/robert-pattinsons-dior-homme-campaign-2017-black-carpet-collection-988503|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除了演戲外，羅拔亦有參與作曲及演奏自己的音樂。他在《[[暮光之城系列|暮光之城系列]]》及2008年獨立喜劇電影《{{le|如何生活|How to Be}}》中也有歌曲獻唱。慈善事業方面，他是ECPAT（終止兒童賣淫、兒童色情及以性目的販運兒童）<ref>[http://www.ecpat.org.uk/media/stars-across-globe-raise-their-hands-stop-child-trafficking/ Stars across the globe raise their hands to stop child trafficking.] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161108195710/http://www.ecpat.org.uk/media/stars-across-globe-raise-their-hands-stop-child-trafficking/ |date=2016-11-08 }}</ref>、父母與兒童共同綁架（PACT）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gpdg.co.uk/pact_old/html/pact_balloons.html |title=PACT團體 |accessdate=2016-11-08 |archive-date=2013-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230234410/http://www.gpdg.co.uk/pact_old/html/pact_balloons.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以及{{le|GO運動|GO Campaign}}的支持者，那是一個非營利組織，旨在提高外界對全世界的孤兒和弱勢兒童的注意及基金援助，他成為後者的2015年大使，以協助提高國際對非營利組織的認識<ref name="#2">{{Cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/robert-pattinson-breaking-dawn-charity-252580 |title='Twilight's' Robert Pattinson Charity Donation to Help Educate Teen Girls in Cambodia |accessdate=2016-11-08 |archive-date=2014-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140306144011/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/robert-pattinson-breaking-dawn-charity-252580 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他亦是國際醫療組織{{le|IMC|International Medical Corps}}的成員，一個由志願醫生和護士建立的全球人道主義非營利組織<ref name="#3">{{Cite web |url=https://internationalmedicalcorps.org/cgi-commitment-to-help-communities-in-humanitarian-disasters#.UsGoedIW2kc |title=International Medical Corps & Global Ambassador Sienna Miller Launch “First Responders” CGI Commitment to Help Communities in Humanitarian Disasters |access-date=2016-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131024043740/https://internationalmedicalcorps.org/cgi-commitment-to-help-communities-in-humanitarian-disasters#.UsGoedIW2kc |archive-date=2013-10-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，並透過「{{le|公共服務公告|Public service announcement}}」推廣及分享有關[[癌症|癌症]]的詳細資料，以提高人們對這種疾病的認識<ref name="#4">{{Cite web |url=https://www.looktothestars.org/news/6753-robert-pattinson-cancer-bites |title=Robert Pattinson: Cancer Bites |access-date=2016-11-08 |archive-date=2021-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303083837/https://www.looktothestars.org/news/6753-robert-pattinson-cancer-bites |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#5">{{Cite web |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/08/08/robert-pattinson-announce_n_920920.html |title=Robert Pattinson Announces Blood Cancer Campaign At Teen Choice Awards |accessdate=2016-11-08 |archive-date=2013-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230234212/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/08/08/robert-pattinson-announce_n_920920.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年，羅拔出演科幻巨作《天能》，飾演尼爾。

== 家庭 ==
羅拔出生於[[英國|英國]][[倫敦|倫敦]]，父親Richard Pattinson從事進口美國中古車的生意，母親Clare任職於模特兒經紀公司<ref>{{cite web |last=Adams |first=Isabelle |url=http://www.harpercollinschildrens.com/HarperChildrens/Kids/BookDetail.aspx?isbn13=9780061765537&BDMode=8 |title=Robert Pattinson |publisher=Harpercollinschildrens.com |accessdate=2010-08-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090428083107/http://www.harpercollinschildrens.com/harperchildrens/kids/bookdetail.aspx?isbn13=9780061765537&bdmode=8 |archivedate=2009-04-28 }}</ref>。羅拔有兩位姐姐，分別為創作歌手{{link-en|Lizzy Pattinson|Lizzy Pattinson}}，及從事廣告製作的Victoria Pattinson<ref name="telegraph">{{cite news|last=Tibbetts|first=Graham|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/celebritynews/3541846/Profile-of-Twilight-star-Robert-Pattinson.html|title=Profile of Twilight star Robert Pattinson|date=2008-12-02|work=The Daily Telegraph|location=UK|accessdate=2009-08-16|archive-date=2010-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100209073258/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/celebritynews/3541846/Profile-of-Twilight-star-Robert-Pattinson.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Glaswegian>{{Cite news|url=http://www.theglaswegian.co.uk/entertainment-lifestyle/2009/11/26/twighlight-star-robert-pattinson-reveals-his-shy-side-102692-21851022|title=Twighlight star Robert Pattinson reveals his shy side|date=2009-11-26|first=Susan|last=Griffin|publisher=The Glaswegian|accessdate=2009-12-04|archive-date=2010-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100220192525/http://www.theglaswegian.co.uk/entertainment-lifestyle/2009/11/26/twighlight-star-robert-pattinson-reveals-his-shy-side-102692-21851022/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

羅拔在[[倫敦|倫敦]]郊區的[[巴恩斯|巴恩斯]]長大<ref name="Biography Today">{{Cite book|title=Biography Today|url=https://archive.org/details/biographytodaypr0000unse|year=2009|page=[https://archive.org/details/biographytodaypr0000unse/page/136 136]|publisher=Omnigraphics|location=[[Detroit|Detroit]], Michigan |isbn=978-0-7808-1052-5}}</ref>，他12歲前就讀於{{link-en|英國塔屋學校|Tower House School}}，然後到{{link-en|哈羅德中學|The Harrodian School}}就讀<ref>"Biography Today", p.136</ref><ref name=Stubbs>{{Cite news|author=Flora Stubbs|title=Potter star 'next Jude Law'|url=http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/film/article-20955856-details/Potter+star+%27next+Jude+Law%27/article.do|publisher=[[Evening_Standard|Evening Standard]]|date=2005-11-17|accessdate=2008-10-02|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080928080552/http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/film/article-20955856-details/Potter+star+%27next+Jude+Law%27/article.do|archivedate=2008-09-28}}</ref>。

== 事業 ==
=== 演藝事業 ===
羅拔中學畢業後加入巴恩斯劇團俱樂部 (Barnes Theatre Club)，參與一些業餘的戲劇演出，最初做雜工，在後台忙了一段時間後，羅拔終獲得了自己的角色，真正的在台上表演。他說：「他們 (巴恩斯劇團俱樂部) 真是個很不錯的團體，當我完成了後台的工作後，我就決定應去嘗試看能否演出某個角色，所以我就去參加了《{{le|紅男綠女|Guys and Dolls}}》的試鏡，獲得了一個非常小的角色，好像是演個古巴跳舞的人，然後在下一次的試鏡是在[[桑顿·怀尔德|桑顿·怀尔德]]的《{{le|Our Town|Our Town}}》飾演George Gibbs，我就當上了主角，然後我就有經理人，所以我真是欠那個俱樂部很多。」

他的演出很快吸引了一家經理人公司的注意，後來該公司便開始為他尋找專業角色的機會。後來，羅拔在[[英國|英國]]的Old Sorting Office Arts Centre參加了《[[Anything_Goes|Anything Goes]]》及《[[Macbeth|Macbeth]]》的業餘演出<ref>"Biography Today", p. 137</ref>。他於製作《[[德伯家的苔丝|黛絲姑娘]]》中飾演一個代理人而受到矚目，自此他便開始尋找專業人士的角色。

==== 2004-2007年：事業早期 ====
2004年，羅拔的第一個銀幕角色是[[電視電影|電視電影]]《{{le|黑暗王朝：魔域屠龍|Dark Kingdom: The Dragon King}}》，當時他演的出一個小配角角色，據説演出這個小配角所賺到的所有收入幾乎都被他用來繳交{{le|哈羅德中學|The Harrodian School}}的學費了。同年，他被[[印度|印度]]女導演[[米拉·奈兒|米拉·奈兒]]看中，參與了名著改編電影《[[浮華新世界|浮華新世界]]》的拍攝，但基於劇情考慮，他的戲份最終全被刪剪，只會在DVD版本中出現<ref>{{cite web|title=The Curse of the Ring (Ring of the Nibelungs) (2004)|url=http://www.michaeldvd.com.au/Reviews/Reviews.asp?ID=6177|accessdate=2013-02-26|archive-date=2016-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314074310/http://michaeldvd.com.au/reviews/reviews.asp?id=6177|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Reese Witherspoon Gushes About Robert Pattinson|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20467098,00.html|accessdate=2013-02-26|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304050250/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20467098,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2005年5月，羅拔在{{le|英國皇家宮廷劇院|Royal Court Theatre}}被提名到於[[英國|英國]]首演的《The Woman Before》但在開幕夜不久前被解僱了，角色由{{le|山姆·萊利|Sam Riley (actor)}}頂上<ref name=STV>{{Cite news|url=http://entertainment.stv.tv/new-moon/whos-who/136806-new-moon-whos-who|title=Robert Pattinson: Teen heartthrob Robert Pattinson is an English actor, model and musician best known for playing vampire Edward Cullen in Twilight|date=2009-11-12|publisher=[[STV_(TV_network)|STV (TV network)]]|accessdate=2009-12-04|archive-date=2009-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091202005247/http://entertainment.stv.tv/new-moon/whos-who/136806-new-moon-whos-who/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年，他被導演選中，在《[[哈利波特：火盃的考驗|哈利波特：火盃的考驗]]》中飾演[[西追·迪哥里|西追·迪哥里]]，三巫鬥法大賽的其中一位鬥士。雖然在戲中，但他的戲分不多且被殺，他的矚目度也不如其他同劇演員來得高，但憑著俊美外表及帶著濃厚歐洲貴族氣息的他，被[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]喻為「英國明日之星<ref>{{cite news|author=Lisa Dillon|title=Almost famous|url=http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/article526398.ece?token=null&offset=0|work=The Times|location=UK|date=2005-05-26|accessdate=2008-10-02|archive-date=2011-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110615113315/http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/article526398.ece?token=null&offset=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>」以及多於一次被喻為[[裘德·洛|裘德·洛]]的接班人<ref name=Stubbs/><ref>{{cite web|title=Top 20 Rising Stars Under 30|url=http://www.snmag.com/MAGAZINE/Features/Top-20-Rising-Stars-Under-30.html|work=[[Saturday_Night_Magazine_(US)|Saturday Night Magazine]]|date=2008-07-29|accessdate=2008-10-02|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080924181516/http://www.snmag.com/MAGAZINE/Features/Top-20-Rising-Stars-Under-30.html|archivedate=2008-09-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Teen People Names 'Artists of the Year' and 'What's Next'|url=http://www.starpulse.com/news/index.php/2005/11/02/teen_people_names_artists_of_the_year_an|publisher=Starpulse|date=2005-11-02|accessdate=2008-10-02|archive-date=2008-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081003131840/http://www.starpulse.com/news/index.php/2005/11/02/teen_people_names_artists_of_the_year_an/|dead-url=no}}</ref>」。

2006年，羅拔在[[BBC_Four|BBC Four]]播出的心理戰慄影片《{{le|The Haunted Airman|The Haunting of Toby Jugg}}》中演出，影片於同年10月31日播出，並獲得好評<ref>{{cite web|title=Review: The Haunted Airman/Dennis Wheatley: A Letter to Posterity|url=http://www.the-medium-is-not-enough.com/2006/11/review_the_haunted_airmandenni.php|accessdate=2013-02-26|archive-date=2013-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130508215117/http://www.the-medium-is-not-enough.com/2006/11/review_the_haunted_airmandenni.php|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The Haunted Airman - a very artsy film reviewed|url=http://blog.monikasulik.net/?p=2087|accessdate=2013-02-26|archive-date=2013-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130522073549/http://blog.monikasulik.net/?p=2087|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.denniswheatley.info/firsteditions05.htm#thotj |title=denniswheatley.info synopsis and information |accessdate=2013-03-22 |archive-date=2013-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130221032956/http://www.denniswheatley.info/firsteditions05.htm#thotj |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[舞台_(報紙)|The Stage]]》讚揚的說：「他飾演的飛行員有著一種青春的驚駭與世間使人厭煩的犬儒主義。<ref>{{cite web|title=The Stage: Review|url=http://www.thestage.co.uk/reviews/review.php/14785/tv-review|accessdate=2013-02-26|archive-date=2014-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141218030812/http://www.thestage.co.uk/reviews/review.php/14785/tv-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>」

2007年2月19日，他出現在一個一集式的電視劇《{{le|壞媽媽手記|The Bad Mother's Handbook}}》中演出一個配角，劇集根據{{le|Kate Long|Kate Long}}的同名暢銷小說而寫的<ref>{{cite web|title=The Bad Mother's Handbook|url=http://www.starz.com/titles/thebadmothershandbook|accessdate=2013-02-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130121035032/http://www.starz.com/titles/TheBadMothersHandbook|archivedate=2013-01-21}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The Bad Mother’s Handbook - rounding off my Robert Pattinson phase|url=http://blog.monikasulik.net/?p=2169|accessdate=2013-02-26|archive-date=2013-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130522085651/http://blog.monikasulik.net/?p=2169|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==== 2008-2013年：暮光系列====
2008年，根據[[史蒂芬妮·梅爾|史蒂芬妮·梅爾]]暢銷同名小說拍攝的浪漫奇幻電影《[[暮光之城：無懼的愛|暮光之城：無懼的愛]]》，羅拔得到一個夢寐以求的角色 - 飾演當中神秘俊美的[[吸血鬼|吸血鬼]][[愛德華·庫倫|愛德華·庫倫]]。據電視周刊《[[电视指南_(美国杂志)|电视指南]]》報導，羅拔最初為[[愛德華·庫倫|愛德華·庫倫]]的試鏡而憂慮，擔心自己不能預期從角色演活那「完美」<ref>{{cite web|title=Before the Spotlight, Twilight's Robert Pattinson Was Intimidated by "Perfect" Role|url=http://movies.tvguide.com/Movie-News/Twilight-Robert-Pattinson-1000071.aspx|work=[[TV_Guide|TV Guide]]|date=2008-11-21|accessdate=2008-11-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090122061432/http://movies.tvguide.com/Movie-News/Twilight-Robert-Pattinson-1000071.aspx|archivedate=2009-01-22}}</ref>。電影最初選角時，女主角早已選定由[[克莉絲汀·史都華|克莉絲汀·史都華]]擔演，但男主角卻遲遲未定案。此時，羅拔由英赴美，去到導演[[凱薩琳·哈德薇克|凱薩琳·哈德薇克]]的家參與試鏡，演出在戲裡的床戲，在5,000名演員中脫穎而出，終獲得愛德華·庫倫一角。電影在2008年11月21日上映，讓羅拔一夜成為電影明星，真正嚐到走紅的滋味<ref>{{cite web|title=Twilight|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/twilight/news/1781117/watch_tonights_twilight_premiere_online/|publisher=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=2012-04-21|archive-date=2015-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403165256/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/twilight/news/1781117/watch_tonights_twilight_premiere_online|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並搖身一變，成為風靡全球的少女殺手的男演員，但他曾於受訪時提到，[[杰克·尼科尔森|傑克·尼克遜]]是他於戲劇表演上的指標，他希望自己能成為能跟他一樣的全方位演技派演員，而非靠著一張漂亮臉皮而獲得少女觀眾的偶像。雖然電影得到的評價不一，但評論者都稱讚他與合演的[[克莉絲汀·史都華|克莉絲汀·史都華]]有微妙的化學作用<ref>{{cite web|title=Reviews|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/twilight/|publisher=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=2012-04-21|archive-date=2009-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091106215543/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/twilight/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》稱羅拔是「有能力及有異國情調的美麗」演員<ref>{{cite web|title=Twilight Review|url=http://movies.nytimes.com/2008/11/21/movies/21twil.html?ref=movies|publisher=New York Times|accessdate=2012-04-21|archive-date=2013-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511185208/http://movies.nytimes.com/2008/11/21/movies/21twil.html?ref=movies|dead-url=no}}</ref>；影評人[[罗杰·埃伯特|羅傑·艾伯特]]稱讚那個角色上，羅拔是「選得好」<ref>{{cite web|title=Twilight Movie Review|url=http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20081119/REVIEWS/811199997|publisher=Roger Ebert|accessdate=2012-04-21|archive-date=2012-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120205154552/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20081119%2FREVIEWS%2F811199997|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，他還是個熱愛運動的人，從足球、田徑到滑雪或是雪上滑板等，皆是他喜愛並精通的運動。但有趣的是，他似乎對棒球不太在行，也因此拍攝電影《[[暮光之城：無懼的愛|暮光之城：無懼的愛]]》時，因不清楚棒球規則，在庫倫家棒球比賽那場戲裡鬧出不少笑話。

同年，羅拔還參與了一齣由{{le|奧利弗·埃文|Oliver Irving}}編寫及執導的低成本喜劇電影《{{le|如何是好|How to Be}}》<ref>{{cite web|title=Robert Pattinson's 'How To Be'|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1607944/robert-pattinsons-how-be-make-tv-debut.jhtml|accessdate=2013-02-26|archive-date=2013-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130514205801/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1607944/robert-pattinsons-how-be-make-tv-debut.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Movie Preview: Robert Pattinson in How To Be|url=http://www.buzzsugar.com/Movie-Preview-Robert-Pattinson-How-3024238|accessdate=2013-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130617105454/http://www.buzzsugar.com/Movie-Preview-Robert-Pattinson-How-3024238|archive-date=2013-06-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，電影於不同的影展中上映，獲得影評人不同的評價<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.slamdance.com/festival/festival/pressreleases/2008winnersannounce.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2008-02-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080129124911/http://www.slamdance.com/festival/festival/pressreleases/2008winnersannounce.html |archivedate=2008-01-29 }} Slamdance Film Festival 2008 Winners</ref><ref name=ricalgary>{{cite web |url=http://www.howtobemovie.com/news/2008/07/mailing-list-3/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-03-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140306192920/http://www.howtobemovie.com/news/2008/07/mailing-list-3/ |archivedate=2014-03-06 }} Further Information on How to Be's appearance at the 2008 Rhode Island and Calgary International Film Festivals</ref>。稍後，他於{{le|保羅·莫里森|Paul Morrison (director)}}執導的西班牙英語劇集《[[達利和他的情人|達利和他的情人]]》中飾演[[薩爾瓦多·達利|薩爾瓦多·達利]]<ref>{{cite web|title=LITTLE ASHES MOVIE WITH ROBERT PATTINSON AS DALI|url=http://teaser-trailer.com/little-ashes-movie-with-robert-pattinson-as-dali/|accessdate=2013-02-26|archive-date=2020-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200221020749/https://teaser-trailer.com/little-ashes-movie-with-robert-pattinson-as-dali/|dead-url=no}}</ref>；他還在Daisy Gili導演的短片《{{le|夏日小屋|The Summer House}}》中演出 <ref>{{cite web|title=Robert Pattinson's Short Film 'The Summer House': Director Daisy Gili Dishes!|url=http://hollywoodcrush.mtv.com/2010/07/09/robert-pattinson-the-summer-house/|accessdate=2013-02-26|archive-date=2015-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150912112001/http://hollywoodcrush.mtv.com/2010/07/09/robert-pattinson-the-summer-house/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，短片後來收錄於《{{le|愛與不信任|Love & Distrust}}》的選集其中一部分重新發布，當中包括5部短片以8個不同文化背景的人，描繪他們對真正滿足的追求<ref>{{cite web|script-title=en:Poster for LOVE & DISTRUST “Starring” Robert Pattinson, Robert Downey Jr., and Sam Worthington|url=http://collider.com/love-and-distrust-movie-poster-robert-pattinson-robert-downey-jr-sam-worthington/|accessdate=2013-02-26|archive-date=2014-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141218025633/http://collider.com/love-and-distrust-movie-poster-robert-pattinson-robert-downey-jr-sam-worthington/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=LOVE & DISTRUST|url=http://www.premierehomevideolexington.com/?p=3078|accessdate=2013-02-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201223745/http://www.premierehomevideolexington.com/?p=3078|archivedate=2014-02-01}}</ref>。 

羅拔在《[[暮光之城：新月|暮光之城：新月]]》中重演[[愛德華·庫倫|愛德華·庫倫]]這個角色，電影於2009年11月20日上映，在開畫周末打破紀錄賺得$142,839,137美元，在全球總賺得$709,827,462美元<ref>{{cite news|title=The Twilight Saga: New Moon Box Office|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=newmoon.htm|accessdate=2012-04-21|newspaper=Box Office Mojo|archive-date=2013-07-12|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6I3KNVNmY?url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=newmoon.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。雖然電影得到負面評價，但《[[芝加哥論壇報|芝加哥論壇報]]》的影評人{{le|邁克爾·菲利普斯|Michael Phillips}}說雖然化妝得很差，但仍然有興趣觀看<ref>{{cite web|title=Movie Reviw|url=http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/talking_pictures/2009/11/the-twilight-saga-new-moon-x-stars.html|publisher=Chicago Tribune|accessdate=2012-04-21|archive-date=2012-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120119012350/http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/talking_pictures/2009/11/the-twilight-saga-new-moon-x-stars.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>；《{{le|阿利桑那共和報|Arizona Republic}}》的{{le|比爾·古德科恩茨|Bill GoodyKoontz}}說雖然羅拔的戲分不多，但有他在的時候他會做到最好<ref>{{cite web|title=New Moon Review|url=http://www.azcentral.com/thingstodo/movies/articles/2009/11/18/20091118newmoon.html#ixzz1sdK7AsTE |publisher=Arizona Republic|accessdate=2012-04-21}}</ref>；《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》的{{le|米高·奧沙利文|Michael O'Sullivan}}指他的演技是一致的強烈<ref>{{cite web|title=Movie Review|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/11/19/AR2009111901239.html|publisher=Washington Post|accessdate=2012-04-21|archive-date=2020-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924234011/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/11/19/AR2009111901239.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

