2009年，羅拔出席第81屆[[奧斯卡頒獎典禮|奧斯卡頒獎典禮]]<ref>{{cite web |author=Josh Horowitz |title=Report: Robert Pattinson To Present At Academy Awards |url=http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2009/02/17/report-robert-pattinson-to-present-at-academy-awards/ |publisher=MTV |date=2009-02-17 |accessdate=2009-08-09 |archive-date=2011-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110205011546/http://moviesblog.mtv.com/2009/02/17/report-robert-pattinson-to-present-at-academy-awards/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2009年11月10日，{{le|英國的Revolver娛樂公司|Revolver Entertainment}}發布了一張[[DVD|DVD]]，紀錄了羅拔生活的細節與受歡迎程度的紀錄片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1623159/story.jhtml|title=Robert Pattinson's Life Is Subject Of 'Robsessed' Documentary|last=Ditzian|first=Eric|date=2009-10-06|work=MTV|accessdate=2009-11-09|archive-date=2009-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091203041108/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1623159/story.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

