2014年5月，兩齣由羅拔主演的電影於《[[第67屆康城影展|康城影展2014]]》上首映<ref>{{cite web|title=Rob Pattinson Stars in Two Cannes Entries: 'Map to the Stars' and 'The Rover' (NEW TRAILER, POSTERS)|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/thompsononhollywood/the-rover-cannes-new-trailer-character-posters|accessdate=2014-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140418220704/http://blogs.indiewire.com/thompsononhollywood/the-rover-cannes-new-trailer-character-posters|archive-date=2014-04-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，首先羅拔主演了[[大衛·米奇歐|大衛·米奇歐]]的未來主義西部電影《{{le|流浪者|The Rover (2014 film)}}》<ref>{{cite news|title=Robert Pattinson To Star In ‘The Rover’|url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/05/robert-pattinson-joins-%E2%80%98the-rover%E2%80%99/|accessdate=2014-08-04|work=Deadline|issue=3 May 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808052423/http://www.deadline.com/2012/05/robert-pattinson-joins-%E2%80%98the-rover%E2%80%99/|archivedate=2014年8月8日}}</ref>，同片還有[[佳·皮雅斯|佳·皮雅斯]]及[[史考特·麥奈利|史葛·麥蘭尼]]<ref>{{cite web|title=‘The Rover’ Teaser Trailer – Robert Pattinson and Guy Pearce Trek Across the Australian Outback|url=http://thefilmstage.com/trailer/the-rover-teaser-trailer-robert-pattinson-and-guy-pearce-trek-across-the-australian-outback/|work=thefilmstage|accessdate=2014-03-01|archive-date=2014-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302222333/http://thefilmstage.com/trailer/the-rover-teaser-trailer-robert-pattinson-and-guy-pearce-trek-across-the-australian-outback/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title='The Rover:' Robert Pattinson FINALLY Wraps Filming in Australia! [PHOTOS]|url=http://au.ibtimes.com/articles/447151/20130318/rover-robert-pattinson-finally-finishes-filming-australia.htm#.Ua30JdL0CHE|website=au.ibtimes.com|accessdate=2013-06-04|archive-date=2013-04-19|archive-url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20130419112126/http://au.ibtimes.com/articles/447151/20130318/rover-robert-pattinson-finally-finishes-filming-australia.htm#.Ua30JdL0CHE|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，電影的首映於影展的比賽中脫穎而出<ref>{{cite web|title='Foxcatcher,' 'Map To The Stars,' 'The Rover,' 'The Search' And New Jean-Luc Godard Lead Cannes 2014 Line-Up|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/foxcatcher-map-to-the-stars-the-rover-the-search-and-new-jean-luc-godard-lead-cannes-2014-line-up-20140417|accessdate=2014-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006132140/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/foxcatcher-map-to-the-stars-the-rover-the-search-and-new-jean-luc-godard-lead-cannes-2014-line-up-20140417|archive-date=2014-10-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。為了演出一個天真的犯罪團隊成員，柏迪臣獲得好評如潮，《{{le|綜藝雜誌|Variety}}》的斯科特·范達斯（Scott Foundas）說：「柏迪臣原來是這部電影的最大驚喜，他體現出一種令人信服的南方口音，並給角色帶出一種低調的尊嚴，這可能很容易被擠成廉價的傷感效果。」他進一步補充說：「他表現出無數深刻的敏感度與感受，這就是柏迪臣演技的重新定義<ref name="Rover review">{{cite news|title=Cannes Film Review: ‘The Rover’|url=https://variety.com/2014/film/reviews/cannes-film-review-the-rover-1201183127/|accessdate=2014-05-19|archive-date=2014-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140518022152/https://variety.com/2014/film/reviews/cannes-film-review-the-rover-1201183127/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」為《[[荷里活報道|荷里活報道]]》寫文章的[[陶德·麥卡錫|陶德·麥卡錫]]寫道，「柏迪臣的表現雖然受到角色本身的限制，但隨著電影的推進而變得更有趣<ref>{{cite news|title=The Rover: Cannes Review|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/rover-cannes-review-704540|accessdate=2014-05-19|archive-date=2014-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140521184222/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/rover-cannes-review-704540|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」替《[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]》寫文章的潔西卡·姜（Jessica Kiang）指，「柏迪臣的表現設法受到的影響比受影響的更大<ref>{{cite news|title=Cannes Review: David Michod's 'The Rover'|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/cannes-review-david-michods-the-rover-20140517|accessdate=2014-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140518223831/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/cannes-review-david-michods-the-rover-20140517|archive-date=2014-05-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。」

接下來，他跟大衛·柯羅能堡於《{{le|寂寞星圖|Maps to the Stars}}》中重聚，那是一齣對荷李活過度嚮往的一齣黑暗漫畫外觀的諷刺劇<ref>{{cite web|title=David Cronenberg's 'Maps to the Stars' Finds Julianne Moore, John Cusack & EOne|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/04/david-cronenberg-julianne-moore-john-cusack-robert-pattinson-maps-to-the-stars-entertainment-one/#|accessdate=2013-06-04|archive-date=2014-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709011907/http://www.deadline.com/2013/04/david-cronenberg-julianne-moore-john-cusack-robert-pattinson-maps-to-the-stars-entertainment-one/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Julianne Moore, John Cusack & Sarah Gadon Join Robert Pattinson in David Cronenberg's 'Map to the Stars'|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/julianne-moore-john-cusack-sarah-gadon-join-robert-pattinson-in-david-cronenbergs-maps-to-the-stars-20130418|accessdate=2013-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130424030004/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/julianne-moore-john-cusack-sarah-gadon-join-robert-pattinson-in-david-cronenbergs-maps-to-the-stars-20130418|archive-date=2013-04-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。電影在[[第67屆康城影展|康城影展2014]]中競逐[[金棕櫚獎|金棕櫚獎]]<ref>{{cite web|title='The Search' And New Jean-Luc Godard Lead Cannes 2014 Line-Up|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/foxcatcher-map-to-the-stars-the-rover-the-search-and-new-jean-luc-godard-lead-cannes-2014-line-up-20140417|accessdate=2014-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006132140/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/foxcatcher-map-to-the-stars-the-rover-the-search-and-new-jean-luc-godard-lead-cannes-2014-line-up-20140417|archive-date=2014-10-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，電影中，他飾演的杰羅姆·豐塔納，是個豪華轎車司機，及希望成為一名成功的編劇而掙扎的演員<ref>{{cite web|title=Maps to the Stars Production Notes|url=http://pathefilms.ch/libraries.files/MTTS_Production_Notes_-_FINAL.pdf|accessdate=2014-04-25|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140424232419/http://pathefilms.ch/libraries.files/MTTS_Production_Notes_-_FINAL.pdf|archivedate=2014年4月24日}}</ref>。《[[每日電訊報|每日電訊報]]》的羅比·科林總結他的表現為「迷人地飾演」<ref name="Tele">{{cite news|title=Cannes 2014, Maps to the Stars, review: 'a nightmare you don't want to wake from'|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/filmreviews/10838381/Cannes-2014-Maps-to-the-Stars-review-a-nightmare-you-dont-want-to-wake-from.html|accessdate=2014-05-19|archive-date=2014-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140519170024/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/filmreviews/10838381/Cannes-2014-Maps-to-the-Stars-review-a-nightmare-you-dont-want-to-wake-from.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年，羅拔的兩齣電影於2月舉行的《[[第65屆柏林影展|第65屆柏林影展]]》上首映，首齣是[[韋納·荷索|韋納·荷索]]執導，改編自[[格特魯德·貝爾|格特魯德·貝爾]]的《{{le|沙漠妖姬|Queen of the Desert (film)}}》，羅拔跟[[妮歌·潔曼|妮歌·潔曼]]及[[占士·法蘭高|占士·法蘭高]]一同演出<ref name="Queen">{{cite news|title=Robert Pattinson Joining Naomi Watts in 'Queen of the Desert'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/robert-pattinson-naomi-watts-queen-desert-361911/|work=The Hollywood Reporter.com|accessdate=2012-08-14|first=Borys|last=Kit|date=2012-08-14|archive-date=2012-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120815190020/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/robert-pattinson-naomi-watts-queen-desert-361911|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Robert Pattinson attached to Herzog's 'Queen'|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118057829|website=Variety.com|publisher=Variety|accessdate=2012-08-14|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120816102142/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118057829|archivedate=2012年8月16日}}</ref>。羅拔在電影中飾演又名為阿拉伯勞倫斯之稱的[[湯瑪斯·愛德華·勞倫斯|湯瑪斯·愛德華·勞倫斯]]，而《[[獨立報|獨立報]]》的杰弗裡·麥克納布（Geoffrey Macnab）形容為「移除了[[彼得·奧圖|彼得·奧圖]]的影子還有一條很長的路要走以及是個漫畫版，他所飾演的阿拉伯勞倫斯是個口齒尖銳的譏諷人物，能夠看穿他的老闆和同事的偽裝的人<ref>{{cite news|title=Queen Of The Desert, review: Werner Herzog's film is like a feminist Lawrence of Arabia|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/reviews/queen-of-the-desert-review-werner-herzogs-film-is-like-a-feminist-lawrence-of-arabia-10029753.html/|work=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|accessdate=2015-02-07|archive-date=2015-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150207075501/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/reviews/queen-of-the-desert-review-werner-herzogs-film-is-like-a-feminist-lawrence-of-arabia-10029753.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」《[[荷里活報道|荷里活報道]]》的大衛·魯尼（David Rooney）稱他的角色為「簡要但重要」並得出結論指「他跟潔曼於場景中的同志情誼是有吸引力的<ref>{{cite web|title='Queen of the Desert': Berlin Review|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/nicole-kidman-werner-herzogs-queen-770806|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|accessdate=2015-02-07|archive-date=2015-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150208035014/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/nicole-kidman-werner-herzogs-queen-770806|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」《[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]》的山姆·亞當斯（Sam Adams）說：「羅拔·柏迪臣演繹真正的人物而獲得相對較高的分數<ref>{{cite web|title=Nicole Kidman and Robert Pattinson in 'Queen of the Desert' Reviews: Herzog's Flat Epic Could Make a Camel Groan|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/criticwire/nicole-kidman-and-robert-pattinson-in-queen-of-the-desert-reviews-herzogs-flat-epic-could-make-a-camel-groan-20150206|website=[[Indiewire|Indiewire]]|accessdate=2015-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150207053924/http://blogs.indiewire.com/criticwire/nicole-kidman-and-robert-pattinson-in-queen-of-the-desert-reviews-herzogs-flat-epic-could-make-a-camel-groan-20150206|archive-date=2015-02-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。」

