接下來，羅拔於[[安東·寇班|安東·寇班]]執導的《[[捕捉占士甸|捕捉占士甸]]》中飾演《[[生活_(雜誌)|生活]]》的攝影師{{le|丹尼斯·史托克|Dennis Stock}}；這部電影涉及他跟演員[[占士·甸|占士·甸]]的友情<ref name="Life">{{cite news|title=Toronto: Robert Pattinson, Dane DeHaan to Star in 'Life'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/toronto-robert-pattinson-dane-dehaan-622421|work=The Hollywood Reporter.com|accessdate=2013-09-06|first=Borys|last=Kit|date=2013-09-05|archive-date=2015-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002095543/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/toronto-robert-pattinson-dane-dehaan-622421|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Pattinson, DeHaan join Life|url=http://www.screendaily.com/news/production/pattinson-dehaan-join-life/5060062.article?blocktitle=LATEST-FILM-NEWS&contentID=40562|website=Deadline.com|accessdate=2013-09-06|archive-date=2013-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130911011845/http://www.screendaily.com/news/production/pattinson-dehaan-join-life/5060062.article?blocktitle=LATEST-FILM-NEWS&contentID=40562|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影的影評招待獲得褒貶不一的影評，然而羅拔卻因為他對攝影師的描繪而獲得了讚賞。《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》的蓋伊·洛奇（Guy Lodge）稱他的表現「轉為狡黠」<ref>{{cite web|title=Berlin Film Review: Anton Corbijn’s ‘Life’|url=https://variety.com/2015/film/reviews/berlin-film-review-anton-corbijns-life-1201427895/|work=Variety|accessdate=2015-02-10|archive-date=2015-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150210094753/http://variety.com/2015/film/reviews/berlin-film-review-anton-corbijns-life-1201427895/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《{{le|善意小謊言|Little White Lies (magazine)}}》指羅拔的表現是跟他角色總是穿著的黑色西裝與白襯衫一樣清脆，這是他對自己問題的一種慢慢地展開來的偽裝，添加顏色和改善整齣電影<ref>{{cite web|title=Berlinale 2015: Life|url=http://www.littlewhitelies.co.uk/features/articles/berlinale-2015-life-29181|accessdate=2015-02-10|website=Little White Lies|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150210091416/http://www.littlewhitelies.co.uk/features/articles/berlinale-2015-life-29181|archivedate=2015年2月10日}}</ref>。《[[荷里活報道|荷里活報道]]》的大衛·魯尼（David Rooney）指，他「給按理說最充分的表現<ref>{{cite web|title='Life': Berlin Review|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/robert-pattinson-dane-dehaan-life-771272?mobile_redirect=false|accessdate=2015-02-10|work=The Hollywood Reporter|archive-date=2015-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150324152917/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/robert-pattinson-dane-dehaan-life-771272?mobile_redirect=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>」。

在2015年末，羅拔出現於[[布拉迪·科貝特|布拉迪·科貝特]]首次執導的電影《{{le|一個領袖的童年|The Childhood of a Leader (film)}}》，同片的有[[贝热尼丝·贝乔|貝妮絲·碧祖]]及[[史黛西·馬汀|史黛西·馬汀]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Berenice Bejo Joins Robert Pattinson Drama ‘The Childhood of a Leader’ (EXCLUSIVE)|url=https://variety.com/2014/film/news/berenice-bejo-the-childhood-of-a-leader-1201287292|work=Variety|accessdate=2014-01-29|archive-date=2014-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140822122038/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/berenice-bejo-the-childhood-of-a-leader-1201287292/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Robert Pattinson to Co-Star in 'The Childhood of a Leader'|url=https://variety.com/2013/biz/news/robert-pattinson-to-co-star-in-the-childhood-of-a-leader-exclusive-1200941925|work=Variety|accessdate=2014-01-29|archive-date=2014-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202094215/http://variety.com/2013/biz/news/robert-pattinson-to-co-star-in-the-childhood-of-a-leader-exclusive-1200941925/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他於電影中飾演雙重角色，首先是[[第一次世界大戰|第一次世界大戰]]時期的德國記者查爾斯·麥卡（Charles Marker），而後者是領袖的成年人版本。他因其表現而受到稱讚，其中《衛報》的彼得·布拉德肖（Peter Bradshaw）稱其為「優雅」<ref>{{cite web|work=The Guardian|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/aug/18/the-childhood-of-a-leader-review-brady-corbet|title=The Childhood of a Leader review – stunning origins story for a future fascist|accessdate=2016-08-19|archive-date=2016-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818222530/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/aug/18/the-childhood-of-a-leader-review-brady-corbet|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而《{{le|國際屏幕|Screen International}}》的李·馬歇爾（Lee Marshall）形容為「優秀」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.screendaily.com/reviews/childhood-of-a-leader-review/5092572.article?referrer=RSS|title='Childhood Of A Leader': Review|accessdate=2015-09-05|work=Screen Daily|archive-date=2015-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905202013/http://www.screendaily.com/reviews/childhood-of-a-leader-review/5092572.article?referrer=RSS|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年，羅拔於《[[失落之城_(電影)|失落之城]]》中亮相，電影由[[派拉蒙影業|派拉蒙影業]]及[[B計劃娛樂|B計劃娛樂]]製作，改編自[[詹姆士·葛雷|占士·葛雷]]的同名小說<ref name="LCOZ">{{cite web|title=Robert Pattinson Joins James Gray's 'Lost City of Z' With Benedict Cumberbatch|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/robert-pattinson-joins-james-grays-lost-city-of-z-with-benedict-cumberbatch-20131106|website=blogs.indiewire.com|accessdate=2013-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216020249/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/robert-pattinson-joins-james-grays-lost-city-of-z-with-benedict-cumberbatch-20131106|archive-date=2013-12-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Watch James Gray’s Chanel Short Film as ‘Lost City of Z’ Adds Charlie Hunnam|url=http://thefilmstage.com/news/watch-james-grays-chanel-short-film-as-lost-city-of-z-adds-charlie-hunnam/|accessdate=2015-02-06|website=The Film Stage|archive-date=2015-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150205210547/http://thefilmstage.com/news/watch-james-grays-chanel-short-film-as-lost-city-of-z-adds-charlie-hunnam/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影於《[[紐約影展|紐約影展]]》中上映，電影講述羅拔飾演的英國探險家亨利·海斯廷（Henry Costin）下士，他為了電影留著一頭厚重的鬍子，以及減重35磅<ref>{{cite web|title=Robert Pattinson Really Hated His "Disgusting" 'Lost City of Z' Beard|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/rambling-reporter/robert-pattinson-hated-his-disgusting-938628|accessdate=2017-03-29|work=The Hollywood Reporter|archive-date=2017-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170330001611/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/rambling-reporter/robert-pattinson-hated-his-disgusting-938628|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的角色獲得影評人的讚譽，《NBP》的馬特·尼格（Matt Neg）稱他為「今天工作的演員中較好的其中一個<ref>{{cite web|title="THE LOST CITY OF Z" REVIEW|url=http://www.nextbestpicture.com/the-lost-city-of-z.html|accessdate=2016-10-17|work=NBP|archive-date=2016-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017222131/http://www.nextbestpicture.com/the-lost-city-of-z.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>」。《布魯克林雜誌（Brooklyn Magazine）》的基思·烏利希（Keith Uhlich）在他的評論中稱他為「微妙場景的小偷<ref>{{cite web|title=#NYFF 2016: The Lost City of Z|url=http://www.bkmag.com/2016/10/17/nyff-2016-lost-city-of-z/|accessdate=2016-10-17|archive-date=2016-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018205447/http://www.bkmag.com/2016/10/17/nyff-2016-lost-city-of-z/|dead-url=no}}</ref>」；而《嘿你們（Heyuguys）》的琳達·馬里克（Linda Marric）發現他的演出是「一個令人印象深刻的微妙場景，但非常精彩<ref>{{cite web|title=Berlinale 2017: The Lost City of Z Review|url=http://www.heyuguys.com/the-lost-city-of-z-review/|website=bkmag.com|accessdate=2017-03-24|archive-date=2017-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170325025346/http://www.heyuguys.com/the-lost-city-of-z-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>」。

隨後，羅拔在{{le|薩夫迪兄弟|Safdie Brothers}}的新-刑房驚悚片《[[失速夜狂奔|失速夜狂奔]]》中演出，飾演銀行劫匪康尼·尼克斯（Connie Nikas）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/robert-pattinson-star-caper-good-807597|title=Robert Pattinson to Star in Caper 'Good Time' (Exclusive)|work=The Hollywood Reporter|accessdate=2015-07-10|archive-date=2015-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150711235904/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/robert-pattinson-star-caper-good-807597|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他稱之為「紐約皇后區真是骨幹的那種精神受損的精神病患者，銀行搶劫電影<ref name="theplaylist.net">{{cite news|title=Robert Pattinson Says He’s Making A "100% Improvised Movie" & Creating Music For A Slapstick Comedy|url=http://theplaylist.net/robert-pattinson-says-hes-making-100-improvised-movie-making-music-slapstick-comedy-20170321/|access-date=2016-03-24|website=The Playlist|archive-date=2017-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170325201655/http://theplaylist.net/robert-pattinson-says-hes-making-100-improvised-movie-making-music-slapstick-comedy-20170321/|dead-url=no}}</ref>」。該片於《[[第70届戛纳电影节|康城影展2017]]》競賽中首映<ref>{{cite web |website=indiewire.com |url=http://www.indiewire.com/2017/04/cannes-2017-lineup-list-film-festival-schedule-1201804813/ |title=2017 Cannes Film Festival Announces Lineup: Todd Haynes, Sofia Coppola, ‘Twin Peaks’ and More |work=IndieWire |date=2017-04-13 |accessdate=2017-04-13 |archive-date=2017-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170714215538/https://www.indiewire.com/2017/04/cannes-2017-lineup-list-film-festival-schedule-1201804813/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而他的表現獲得評論家的一致讚揚。《綜藝雜誌》的蓋伊·洛奇（Guy Lodge）稱他的表現是他的「事業高峰期<ref>{{cite web|title=Cannes Film Review: Robert Pattinson in ‘Good Time’|url=https://variety.com/2017/film/festivals/good-time-cannes-review-robert-pattinson-1202426336/|accessdate=2017-05-25|archive-date=2017-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170525124352/http://variety.com/2017/film/festivals/good-time-cannes-review-robert-pattinson-1202426336/|dead-url=no}}</ref>」；《Indiewire》的Eric Kohn稱之為「他的職業生涯中的最佳<ref>{{cite web|title=Robert Pattinson Gives a Career-Best Performance in the Safdie Brothers’ ‘Good Time’ — Cannes 2017 Review|url=http://www.indiewire.com/2017/05/good-time-review-robert-pattinson-cannes-1201818268/|accessdate=2017-05-25|archive-date=2017-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170525120948/http://www.indiewire.com/2017/05/good-time-review-robert-pattinson-cannes-1201818268/|dead-url=no}}</ref>」；而《荷李活報道》的大衛·魯尼（David Rooney）把他與[[阿爾·柏仙奴|阿爾·柏仙奴]]的《[[黃金萬兩|黃金萬兩]]》中桑尼·華吉克（Sonny Wortzik）作比較，並最終將其稱為「迄今為止他的表現最出色之作<ref>{{cite web|title='Good Time': Film Review Cannes 2017|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/good-time-review-cannes-2017-1004988|accessdate=2017-05-25|archive-date=2017-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170525111351/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/good-time-review-cannes-2017-1004988|dead-url=no}}</ref>」。

