ssdate=2017-08-11|archive-date=2017-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170811012027/http://www.indiewire.com/2017/08/robert-pattinson-hot-dog-short-video-1201865374/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

