=== 音樂 ===
除了演員這個身份之外，自幼學琴的羅拔·柏迪臣也是個優秀的音樂家，他於出道前曾在家鄉組過樂隊，並在餐廳與俱樂部等地方演出過。他擅長玩結他和鋼琴，還會撰寫自己的音樂作品<ref>{{cite web|title=Robert Pattinson: 'I'm Really Not That Interesting'|url=http://www.theimproper.com/Template_Article.aspx?IssueId=10&ArticleId=3071|publisher=The Improper|accessdate=2009-02-01|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090204092005/http://www.theimproper.com/Template_Article.aspx?IssueId=10&ArticleId=3071|archivedate=2009-02-04}}</ref>。電影《如何是好》的配樂是取自羅拔主唱的3首原創歌曲<ref>{{cite web|title=Robert Pattinson Sings Three Songs in Indie Flick How to Be|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/news/robert-pattinson-sings-in-indie-flick-how-to-be-2009313|publisher=Us Magazine|date=2009-03-11|accessdate=2009-03-31|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090403073201/http://www.usmagazine.com/news/robert-pattinson-sings-in-indie-flick-how-to-be-2009313|archivedate=2009-04-03}}</ref>，由作曲人喬·哈斯丁（Joe Hastings）寫成的<ref>{{cite web|title=Songs composed by Joe Hastings in Indie Flick How to Be|url=http://www.howtobemovie.com/soundtrack|publisher=How to Be|date=2009-03-09|accessdate=2009-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090330040247/http://www.howtobemovie.com/soundtrack/|archive-date=2009-03-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。除了錄製原聲配樂之外，羅拔說：「我從未真正的記錄任何東西 - 我只是在酒吧和其他東西上玩」，當被問及專業的音樂事業時，他說：「如果我的演員生涯失敗的時候，音樂就是我的後備計劃<ref name="LA Times"/>。」

他在《[[暮光之城|暮光之城]]原聲碟》中有兩首歌曲是由他主唱，分別是與森姆·布拉德利（Sam Bradley）合寫的《Never Think》<ref>{{cite web|title=Sam Bradley Interview|url=http://www.portraitmagazine.net/interviews/sambradley.html|publisher=Portrait Magazine|date=December 2008|accessdate=2009-01-30|archive-date=2012-09-10|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120910000734/http://www.portraitmagazine.net/interviews/sambradley.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，以及跟馬庫斯·福斯特（Marcus Foster）和波比·朗（Bobby Long）一起合寫的《Let Me Sign》<ref>{{cite web|author=Becky Reed|title=Twilight Star Talks Soundtrack|url=http://www.clickmusic.com/articles/9942/Twilight-Star-Talks-Soundtrack.html|publisher=Click Music|accessdate=2009-01-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090126075841/http://www.clickmusic.com/articles/9942/Twilight-Star-Talks-Soundtrack.html|archivedate=2009-01-26}}</ref>。導演[[凱瑟琳·哈德威克|凱瑟琳·哈德威克]]在電影的早期剪輯中加入了羅拔在不知情的情況下之錄音，他同意指「其中一首歌很具體，它真的令現場場景的氣氛更好，那裡似乎認為應該要有的<ref name="LA Times"/>」，於是歌曲最終被納入在電影中。

在2010年，羅拔在頒獎典禮中獲得《荷李活最具影響力的意想不到音樂人》的獎項<ref>{{cite web|title=Robert Pattinson Awarded Musical Honour|url=http://www.mtv.co.uk/robert-pattinson/news/robert-pattinson-awarded-musical-honour|website=MTV UK|publisher=MTV|date=2010-05-07|accessdate=2014-06-06|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714155628/http://www.mtv.co.uk/robert-pattinson/news/robert-pattinson-awarded-musical-honour|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

而羅拔的姊姊Lizzy也是位傑出的創作歌手，曾跟[[Aurora|Aurora]]樂隊登上十大跳舞歌曲的榜首。

2017年3月，羅拔在一個訪問中確認於電影《{{link-en|少女 (電影)|Damsel (2018 film)|少女}}》中曾作出音樂上的貢獻<ref>{{cite news|title=Rob's weird world|url=http://edition.metro.news/content/20170315.am/htmlpages/537791.html|access-date=2016-03-15|work=Metro News|archive-date=2017-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170614080237/https://edition.metro.news/content/20170315.am/htmlpages/537791.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。談到關於這個事情，他說：「儘管我正在為電影做音樂，但我不再玩那麼多了。我需要區分音樂和演戲，但更多的是我不玩音樂，我越是把大腦的這個領域推向演戲，我玩的音樂就如即興創作<ref name="theplaylist.net"/>。」

=== 慈善事業 ===
慈善事業方面，羅拔·柏迪臣是支持並促進英國{{le|終止兒童賣淫和販運|End Child Prostitution and Trafficking}}的運動，以阻止兒童及青少年作性目的販運，以及停止販賣人口<ref name="ecpat">{{cite web|title=Stars across the globe raise their hands to stop child trafficking|url=http://www.ecpat.org.uk/media/stars-across-globe-raise-their-hands-stop-child-trafficking|accessdate=2013-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230232257/http://www.ecpat.org.uk/media/stars-across-globe-raise-their-hands-stop-child-trafficking|archive-date=2013-12-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Stop Sex Trafficking Campaign|url=http://www.childrensrights.ie/whats-new/stop-sex-trafficking-campaign|accessdate=2013-12-30|archive-date=2013-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230234934/http://www.childrensrights.ie/whats-new/stop-sex-trafficking-campaign|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Robert Pattinson And Others Raise Their Hands For Charity|url=http://www.looktothestars.org/news/4758-robert-pattinson-and-others-raise-their-hands-for-charity|accessdate=2013-12-30|archive-date=2013-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230235031/http://www.looktothestars.org/news/4758-robert-pattinson-and-others-raise-their-hands-for-charity|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在《[[第62屆康城影展|第62屆康城影展]]》的{{le|愛滋病研究基金會|amfAR, The Foundation for AIDS Research}}上，他為此籌募了56,000美元<ref>{{cite web|title=Pucker up for a pricey Robert Pattinson kiss|url=http://www.today.com/id/30885815#.UsGgQNIW2kc|accessdate=2013-12-30|archive-date=2013-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231001209/http://www.today.com/id/30885815#.UsGgQNIW2kc|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年6月，他將自己的作品放到[[eBay|eBay]]上拍賣，然後把收益捐到{{le|父母與被綁架兒童團體|Parents and Abducted Children Together}}<ref name="gpdg">{{cite web|title=BID NOW in PACT's celebrity art auction!|url=http://www.gpdg.co.uk/pact_old/html/pact_balloons.html|accessdate=2013-12-30|archive-date=2013-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230234410/http://www.gpdg.co.uk/pact_old/html/pact_balloons.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="#6">{{cite web|title=Robert Pattinson's Balloon Design Goes Under The Hammer For Charity|url=http://www.looktothestars.org/news/4822-robert-pattinsons-balloon-design-goes-under-the-hammer-for-charity|accessdate=2013-12-30|archive-date=2013-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230233859/http://www.looktothestars.org/news/4822-robert-pattinsons-balloon-design-goes-under-the-hammer-for-charity|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以幫助該組織失蹤兒童進行工作<ref name="gpdg"/><ref name="#6"/>。他還捐贈了一幅自己繪畫的素描，名為《未完成的城市》，拍賣價格為6,400美元<ref>{{cite web|title='Unfinished City'|url=http://www.homeplateproject.com/plates/plate26.php|accessdate=2013-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231011159/http://www.homeplateproject.com/plates/plate26.php|archive-date=2013-12-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。拍賣行提其所賣得的金錢捐到以亞利桑那州為基礎的無家可歸者中心「奧茲安南莊園」<ref>{{cite web|title=Robert Pattinson, A Pencil, A Sketch And The Homeless: Raising Arizona|url=http://www.inquisitr.com/318640/robert-pattinson-a-pencil-a-sketch-and-the-homeless-raising-arizona|accessdate=2013-12-30|archive-date=2013-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230234052/http://www.inquisitr.com/318640/robert-pattinson-a-pencil-a-sketch-and-the-homeless-raising-arizona/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2011年1月，他主動請纓參與了慈善機構的馬拉松式電視節目《{{le|海地現在的希望：全球抗震救災活動|Hope for Haiti Now: A Global Benefit for Earthquake Relief}}》<ref>{{cite web|title=Robert Pattinson Speaks At 'Hope For Haiti Now' Telethon: Use Technology To Help Haiti Crisis|url=http://hollywoodcrush.mtv.com/2010/01/22/robert-pattinson-speaks-at-hope-for-haiti-now-telethon-use-technology-to-help-haiti-crisis|accessdate=2013-12-30|archive-date=2013-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230234950/http://hollywoodcrush.mtv.com/2010/01/22/robert-pattinson-speaks-at-hope-for-haiti-now-telethon-use-technology-to-help-haiti-crisis/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="mtv-liveblog">{{cite web|url=http://newsroom.mtv.com/2010/01/22/hope-for-haiti-live-blog|date=2010-01-22|title=Hope For Haiti Now: A Global Benefit For Earthquake Relief|first=Kyle|last=Anderson|work=[[MTV_News|MTV News]]|accessdate=2010-01-23|archive-date=2010-03-09|archive-url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20100309012017/http://newsroom.mtv.com/2010/01/22/hope-for-haiti-live-blog/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2011年3月，他把已簽名的結他拍賣所得的錢，捐到{{le|午夜使命|Midnight Mission}}<ref>{{cite web|title=ROBERT PATTINSON AUCTIONS OFF SIGNED GUITAR FOR HOMELESS CHARITY|url=http://earsucker.com/robert-pattinson-auctions-off-signed-guitar-for-homeless-charity|accessdate=2013-12-30|archive-date=2013-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131230232906/http://earsucker.com/robert-pattinson-auctions-off-signed-guitar-for-homeless-charity/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="guitar charity">{{cite web|url=http://www.gossipcop.com/perez-strikes-bad-chord-with-Robert-pattinson-guitar-story|date=2010-03-18|title=Perez strikes bad chord with Robert Pattinson guitar story|work=[[Gossip_Cop|Gossip Cop]]|publisher=Gossip Cop|accessdate=2010-03-18|archive-date=2010-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100323003809/http://www.gossipcop.com/perez-strikes-bad-chord-with-robert-pattinson-guitar-story/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他是{{le|GO運動|GO Campaign}}的支持者，那是一個非營利組織，旨在提高外界對全世界的孤兒和弱勢兒