自《[[暮光之城系列|暮光之城系列]]》於2008年開始拍攝以後，羅拔·柏迪臣的名字與同片女星[[姬絲汀·史超域|姬絲汀·史超域]]浪漫地連結著<ref>{{cite web|last=Duncan|first=Amy|title=Spotted! Robert Pattinson and Kristen Stewart spark fresh dating rumours|url=http://www.metro.co.uk/showbiz/861173-robert-pattinson-and-kristen-stewart-spark-fresh-dating-rumours|work=Metro|accessdate=2012-03-09|archive-date=2012-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120825231559/http://www.metro.co.uk/showbiz/861173-robert-pattinson-and-kristen-stewart-spark-fresh-dating-rumours|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在一直以來拍攝整個電影系列的時間中，他們倆都沒有明確地確認彼此的關係，但娛樂雜誌狗仔隊拍得的相片，與目擊者帶動激烈的傳媒和支持者的推測與關注<ref>{{cite web|title=Robert Pattinson: why are Twilight fans so weird?|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/twilight/8371653/Robert-Pattinson-why-are-Twilight-fans-so-weird.html|work=Telegraph|accessdate=2013-06-20|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201044032/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/twilight/8371653/Robert-Pattinson-why-are-Twilight-fans-so-weird.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Robert Pattinson and Kristen Stewart put on united front for Twilight fans|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/robert-pattinson-and-kristen-stewart-put-on-united-front-for-twilight-fans-8312193.html|work=Independent.co.uk|accessdate=2013-06-20|archive-date=2013-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130724013249/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/robert-pattinson-and-kristen-stewart-put-on-united-front-for-twilight-fans-8312193.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，使二人名字合成"Rob-sten"，並使之成為媒體廣泛報導的對象主題<ref name=GQ>{{cite web|last=Heaf|first=Jonathan|title=Blood Lust|url=http://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/girls/articles/2011-10/03/gq-girls-kristen-stewart-british-gq-cover-pictures-twilight-breaking-dawn/photos|work=GQ|accessdate=2012-03-09|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120114114208/http://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/girls/articles/2011-10/03/gq-girls-kristen-stewart-british-gq-cover-pictures-twilight-breaking-dawn/photos|archivedate=2012-01-14}}</ref>。然而，姬絲汀·史超域在2012年7月首次正式公開承認跟羅拔·柏迪臣的情侶關係後不久後，被雜誌《{{le|Us Weekly雜誌|Us Weekly}}》刊登了她跟電影《[[白雪公主與獵人|白雪公主與獵人]]》的導演[[路柏·山達斯|路柏·山達斯]]，而《[[赫芬頓郵報|赫芬頓郵報]]》顯示二人有私情<ref>{{cite news|title=Kristen Stewart's Cheating Apology: PR Insider Weighs In|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/katie-calautti/kristen-stewarts-cheating-scandal_b_1703774.html|work=Huffington Post|accessdate=2012-07-26|first=Katie|last=Calautti|date=2012-07-25|archive-date=2013-02-06|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6EDx5DLH6?url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/katie-calautti/kristen-stewarts-cheating-scandal_b_1703774.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url= http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hollywood/news-interviews/Pattinson-heartbroken-after-Stewarts-cheating-scandal/articleshow/15188510.cms| title= Pattinson heartbroken after Stewart's cheating scandal| date= 2012-07-27}}{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Kristen Stewart's Apology to Robert Pattinson for Cheating|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20614722,00.html|publisher=People Magazine|accessdate=2012-07-25|archive-date=2013-02-06|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6EDx49RIs?url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20614722,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Kristen Stewart's Cheating Apology: PR Insider Weighs In|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/katie-calautti/kristen-stewarts-cheating-scandal_b_1703774.html|publisher=Huffington Post|accessdate=2012-07-26|first=Katie|last=Calautti|date=2012-07-25|archive-date=2013-02-06|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6EDx5DLH6?url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/katie-calautti/kristen-stewarts-cheating-scandal_b_1703774.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。照片被刊出當天，姬絲汀·史超域於《[[人物_(雜誌)|人物 (雜誌)]]》向羅拔發表了公開道歉：「我對於由我引起對身邊人和每個受影響的人，他們傷害與難堪深感抱歉，此一時的輕率已經危及到我生命中最重要的事情，我最愛和最尊敬的人，羅拔，我愛他，我愛他，我很對不起<ref>Jordan, Julie; Schwartz, Alison. [http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20614722,00.html "Kristen Stewart's Apology to Robert Pattinson for Cheating"] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6EDx49RIs?url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20614722,00.html |date=20130206072914 |dateformat=iso }}, ''People'', 25 July 2012; accessed 13 June 2014.</ref>。」在一番迴避重複問題之後，羅拔於2014年7月在《英國時尚先生》的訪談節目中確認他跟姬絲汀·史超域於2012年分手<ref>{{cite news|title=Robert Pattinson gives first TV interview since split from Kristen Stewart|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/celebritynews/9474813/Robert-Pattinson-gives-first-TV-interview-since-split-from-Kristen-Stewart.html|work=The Guardian|accessdate=2014-09-18|first=Rosa|last=Silverman|date=2012-08-14|archive-date=2019-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190829100219/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/celebritynews/9474813/Robert-Pattinson-gives-first-TV-interview-since-split-from-Kristen-Stewart.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Robert Pattinson: Exclusive Interview For Esquire September Issue|url=http://www.esquire.co.uk/culture/film-tv/6735/robert-pattinson-interview-esquire-cover-star|work=Esquire UK|accessdate=2014-09-18|first=Sanjiv|last=Bhattacharya|date=2014-07-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140921173352/http://www.esquire.co.uk/culture/film-tv/6735/robert-pattinson-interview-esquire-cover-star/|archivedate=2014年9月21日}}</ref>。在此之前，曾有報導猜測二人於2013年5月分手，當時有人目睹羅拔·柏迪臣從姬絲汀·史超域的家中取走其私人物品<ref>{{cite news|title=Robert Pattinson Moves Stuff Out of Kristen Stewart's House, Leaves With His Dogs|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/420886/robert-pattinson-moves-stuff-out-of-kristen-stewart-s-house-leaves-with-his-dogs|website=E Online|accessdate=2014-09-29|first=Natalie|last=Finn|date=2013-05-20|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006150918/http://www.eonline.com/news/420886/robert-pattinson-moves-stuff-out-of-kristen-stewart-s-house-leaves-with-his-dogs|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

